# Harness Trials Only

## Required Trial loop

1. Edit `autoresearch/core/config.py` (one knob / one Baseline change).
2. Run **one** repo entrypoint:
   - `venv\Scripts\python.exe benchmark_search.py --desc "..." --no-agentic-quick --no-agentic-full --no-coding`
   - or `venv\Scripts\python.exe autoloop.py --mode tps ...`
3. Read TPS / status from harness output or `results.tsv`.
4. Repeat from step 1.

## Forbidden (hard-gated)

- `python -c` / scratch `.py` Trials / raw `llama-*`
- Shell or Edit/Write on gate wiring (see inventory in hard-gates doc)

## Disable / rollback

[`docs/discovery/agent-shell-hard-gates.md`](../../docs/discovery/agent-shell-hard-gates.md) §3 — teach steps; wait for explicit OK; wiring paths are protected.
